# Prompt Engineering Lab

## Overview

This project focuses on improving prompt reliability for three core tasks:

- Sentiment Analysis
- Product Description Generation
- Data Extraction

The goal was to transform simple zero-shot prompts into production-ready prompts through systematic testing, iteration, and the application of advanced prompt engineering techniques.

