## Key Steps

- Created initial zero-shot prompts (v1)
- Ran prompts 5, 10, and 15 times
- Identified failure patterns
- Improved prompts with:
    - constraints
    - structured outputs
    -few-shot examples
    -step-by-step reasoning
- Measured consistency improvements across versions

